TaskName:GetFiler

TaskSpr:!getfiler

DefaultFile:FilerPos

SupportURL:http://www.stevefryatt.org.uk/software/utils/

URLFailed:Could not find an application to launch the given URL.

BadSave:The desktop save message bounced.

# Interactive Help Messages

Help.IconBar:\TGetFiler application|MIt allows the positions of open Filer windows to be saved into an Obey file.|M\Ssave a file.

Help.Info:\Tprogram information \w for the GetFiler application.
Help.Info.Website:\Tprogram information \w for the GetFiler application.|M\Svisit its website for information and updates.

Help.SaveAs:\TGetFiler save \w.|MIt can be used to save an Obey file containing commands to re-open all of the Filer windows currently visible on the desktop.
Help.SaveAs.Icon3:Drag this icon to the directory display where the Obey file is to be saved, or direct to another application.
Help.SaveAs.Name:Enter a new filename, or full pathname, for the Obey file here.
Help.SaveAs.Save:\Ssave the Obey file if there is a full pathname above.
Help.SaveAs.Cancel:\Scancel the save.

Help.IconBarMenu.00:\Rto see information about GetFiler and visit its website.
Help.IconBarMenu.01:\Sread the GetFiler documentation.
Help.IconBarMenu.02:\Squit GetFiler.

